DESCRIPTION
The Streets of New Capenna Set Booster Box contains 30 Streets of New Capenna Set Boosters and 1 traditional foil box topper card. Each Set Booster contains 12 Magic cards, 1 Art Card, and 1 token, ad card, counter punchout card, or special card from Magic's history (a card from "The List").
